1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper deals with generating composite images from object images, which is a core problem in computer vision.
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a novel self-consistent Composition-by-Decomposition (CoDe) network to compose a pair of objects, which involves machine learning techniques.
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes a method to capture complex interactions between different objects in the world, which is a key problem in AI.
4. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper deals with generating realistic composite images, which is a core problem in computer graphics.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with generating composite images, which is a multimedia application.
